@DATABASE "The Spy Who Loved Me"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - T - The Spy Who Loved Me"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - T
                   ====================================

                           The Spy Who Loved Me
                           ====================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(36185,0)"}          36185,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(35055,255) zxampoke(34010,255)"}          35055,x:34010,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Immunity Lev 1" rxs "address command zxampoke(36107,0)"}          36107,0



                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
